title: Springfield of Dreams The Legend of Homer Simpson
description: Springfield of Dreams The Legend of Homer Simpson This one-hour special honors the legacy of the third-season episode "Homer at the Bat", featuring interviews from some of the episode's guest stars and six minutes of never-before seen footage of the show. October 22, 2017 A comedic "Simpsonized" documentary celebrating the legendary episode "Homer at the Bat" and Homer's induction into the National Baseball Hall of Fame. Features interviews with baseball players, historians, and sportscasters. http://www.imdb.com/title/tt7530988/
